  "detailed_description": "Dive into the serene world of AquaFantasia, an engaging and soothing idle game.Begin your aquatic adventure by purchasing a variety of small fry, raise and sell them. You can customize fantasy oceans with rare fishes to create your own aquarium.<br><br>Epic fish can lead their kind to wander in the ocean, while legendary fish can become the leaders of all fish.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/ad2914f75b38fe5f3c8894a4f8a02eaf.poster.avif?t=1715227470\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/ad2914f75b38fe5f3c8894a4f8a02eaf.webm?t=1715227470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/ad2914f75b38fe5f3c8894a4f8a02eaf.mp4?t=1715227470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Purchase fry packs to unlock rare fish.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/4054e5f7d9fcba80f5f052ef08eb3c76.poster.avif?t=1715227470\" width=550 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/4054e5f7d9fcba80f5f052ef08eb3c76.webm?t=1715227470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/4054e5f7d9fcba80f5f052ef08eb3c76.mp4?t=1715227470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Feed the fish, or select one to play with it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2924890/extras/2e6b0c07eca2d0a742a6ca3aa64f2cb1.poster.avif?t=1715227470\" width=550 height=308 ><sou